title: 04/26/21 DPS Hour 3 Alex Smith
itunes:title: 04/26/21 DPS Hour 3 Alex Smith
description:
Alex Smith tells Dan that he is looking forward to being able to being around family because he never had time while playing in the NFL. Alex says he is in a good place, but does not know what he will be like on Sunday in September without football.
